{"tid":1821501,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［支持藍色經濟圈］決定同 元氣，吉野家 手足齊上齊落！！！","createTime":"2020-01-12T10:53:36.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-13T00:14:03.000Z","uid":161417,"like":16,"dislike":78,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"ba80630bce0d40106f9fe7ca65dcfd330dd8fbb7","tid":1821501,"uid":161417,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-12T10:53:36.000Z","msg":"一手FC咗，原來元氣，吉野家大部分都係自己手足黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n對住佢地叫五大訴求，佢地會叫缺一不可嫁 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n其中有好多元氣手足仲同我講，佢地都係前線學生，D錢買曬GEAR先窮到百幾蚊食一餐元氣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n超可憐 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n所以還押緊, 坐緊監既手足對唔住啦<br />\n我地香港人決定同元氣，吉野家入面既手足齊上齊落<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔攬炒經濟了<br />\n始於影人大頭會失民意嫁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n支持大家入去幫襯元氣 吉野家，陪手足一齊食， 齊上齊落！！！　<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static7.orstatic.com/userphoto2/photo/11/TFU/05TCRQ5D44E0EA7461D0A8px.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic7.orstatic.com%2Fuserphoto2%2Fphoto%2F11%2FTFU%2F05TCRQ5D44E0EA7461D0A8px.jpg&h=672e40bd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n先貼為敬<br />\n今日我特登入咗去元氣叫個下午茶，入面有五件壽司<br />\n代表五大訴求　缺一不可<br />\n大家唔好影我大頭，香港人齊上齊落！！！　<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"adff0e4b91a69f10646dbb5971f3bfda95cb1e0f","tid":1821501,"uid":161417,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-12T10:54:17.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"82775befac484ead30f37ff9137043bc43170939","tid":1821501,"uid":161417,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-12T10:54:41.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"cbaf95222fff37ad28f1785f364845f975ea42e0","tid":1821501,"uid":161417,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-12T10:55:06.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"09a2f090727abb76d7de8d57205319b877e1dce3","tid":1821501,"uid":38904,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-12T10:55:30.000Z","msg":"開錯台？"},{"pid":"baea4edcd428d9b3a5235cdd7bad233bd102d76b","tid":1821501,"uid":161417,"like":5,"dislike":9,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-12T10:59:19.000Z","msg":"講返起Ｄ裝修師其實都有Ｄ唔啱<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n點解藍到黑既店就要裝修？<br />\n政見唔同就可以裝修？<br />\n仲有好多人係想食藍店嫁　<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n抵坐監真係，你地批鬥自己人就叻　<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"302242f77cad7395730dab11a098e2d7f0832735","tid":1821501,"uid":158889,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-12T11:00:11.000Z","msg":"真 元朗藍絲曲線幫你地宣傳721 <br />\n<br />\n直頭手足 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ecdb8002d809f8d2dab8a4e1033317189192b4bc","tid":1821501,"uid":161505,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTim